name: Couple NFTs - Pair #1 - I am Yours
description: Couple NFTS are my creations that have only 2 editions. Thus, only two of this design will exist in the whole world. These are meant for couples. Like the way couples wear couple shirts, I hope my couple NFTs will also be a way of showing love to your beloved. You can just buy one for yourself and try to find the one who has the same design, hoping you would be a couple. Or, if you already have someone special, you can buy the pair and give one to your beloved. This design is a heart radiating love saying, "I am yours."
